    Create Session  httpbin  http://httpbin.org    debug=3
    ${resp}=  Get Request  httpbin  /redirect/1
    Should Be Equal As Strings  ${resp.status_code}  200

    ${resp}=  Get Request  httpbin  /redirect/1  allow_redirects=${true}
    Should Be Equal As Strings  ${resp.status_code}  200

